Dax, a Canadian rapper has tattooed the Nigerian flag on his neck to prove that his roots are from Nigeria. “Show less do more” were the words inscribed close to his tattoo. Mixed reactions were evoked after the rapper took to the bird app to show his fans that he is a Nigerian. He garnered accolades from many people who were able to chance upon his new ink on social media. They lauded him for his patriotic gesture. NEW TATTOO: ?? Yes. I am NIGERIAN. pic.twitter.com/po2ngWOM8G — Dax (@thatsdax) April 2, 2021